    "body": "\u30fb`PerlPackage` uses setting information in `config_heavy.pl` for generating `Makefile` from `Makefile.PL`.\r\n\u30fb`spack_cflags` specified when installing`PerlPackage` doesn't take in `Makefile`.\r\nSo, I fixed the `perl` package file so that `spack_cflags` are taken in `config_heavy.pl` when installing `perl`.",
